window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Is anxiety holding you back from your goals or personal relationships? Are you tired of fearing failure and worrying all of the time? We all need peace and relaxation, and now you can live anxiety-free with this hypnosis album from Amy Applebaum Hypnosis. </p> <p>Amy is a world-renowned life coach, NLP trainer, and Time-line Therapist, who has taken her knowledge of success, both business and personal, and created this hypnosis program to help you release from negative blocks and help you reach your life goals. </p> <p>You deserve to have peace and relaxation, and hypnosis can help. Positive suggestions and binaural beats will be received by your mind, releasing stress and tension and deeply relaxing the mind and body. </p> <p> “Be Anxiety Free” promotes inner peace, guided meditation, and deep relaxation. Why wait another day? Get rid of the stress and embrace a healing, peaceful lifestyle. </p> <p>This album contains hypnosis instructions, two different inductions with optional “sleep” or “wake” endings, relaxing music, and affirmations and actions for change: </p> <p>Track 1 - Hypnosis Instructions<br>Track 2 - Relaxation Induction – Wake Ending<br>Track 3 - Relaxation Induction – Sleep Ending<br>Track 4 - Seashore Induction - Wake Ending<br>Track 5 - Seashore Induction – Sleep Ending<br>Track 6 - Meditation Music<br>Track 7 - Deep Sleep Music<br>Track 8 - Relaxation Music<br>Track 9 - Daily Affirmations for Change<br>Track 10 - Actions for Change </p> <p>For more information on Amy Applebaum and her products, please visit http://www.amyapplebaumalbums.com</p>"; 
